These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################
 
